  "name": "Morrison COU2 \u2014 VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This UnitOfAssurance evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use scope \u2014 Class III VAD hemolysis prediction for regulatory submission at operating conditions of 3000\u20136000 RPM and 2\u20138 L/min flow \u2014 is described in the bound Requirement and Claim nodes. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed; all 13 credibility factors have been assessed under the MRL-5 requirements. Decision: Accepted on the basis that all assessed factors meet or exceed required gradation levels under the Minimal profile criteria.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-cfd-hemolysis-class3-vad",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v2",
