    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been assessed and each achieves a gradation level meeting or exceeding the required level for Model Risk Level 5 under the Minimal profile. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is fully propagated. The Claim \u2014 that CFD can predict absolute NIH for the FDA generic centrifugal pump as a surrogate for Class III VAD hemolysis assessment \u2014 is supported by the evidence package. The intended use scope (Class III VAD, 3000\u20136000 RPM, 2\u20138 L/min, regulatory submission context) is articulated in the bound Requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-vad-hemolysis-mrl5) and Claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-cfd-hemolysis-class3-vad) nodes. Decision: Accepted.",
